<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Start Here — Learn Java Step by Step</title>

  <!-- SEO -->
  <meta name="description" content="A simple step-by-step path to learn Java from scratch to building your first assignment. Clean, structured, and easy to follow.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="learn Java, Java basics, Java tutorial, JFrame, beginner programming, coding lessons">
  <meta name="author" content="Dylan Gorrah">

  <!-- Open Graph (for sharing) -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="Start Here — Learn Java Step by Step">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Follow a clean, simple path from Java basics to building your first real assignment.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://dylan-gorrah.github.io/">

  <!-- Mobile Theme Color -->
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f0f10">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f0f10;
      --text: #eaeaea;
      --muted: #888;
      --accent: #ffffff;
    }

    body.light {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --text: #111;
      --muted: #666;
      --accent: #000;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Glass top bar */
    .topbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    body.light .topbar {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .toggle {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .toggle:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    body.light .toggle {
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 80px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .link {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }

    body.light .link {
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .link:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .link:active {
      transform: scale(0.97);
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }

    body.light .footer {
      color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    /* Floating particles */
    .particle {
      position: fixed;
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: float 20s linear infinite;
    }

    body.light .particle {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    @keyframes float {
      from {
        transform: translateY(100vh);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      10% { opacity: 1; }
      to {
        transform: translateY(-10vh);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }

    /* Scrollbar */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 6px;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
      background: transparent;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    body.light ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="toggle" onclick="toggleMode()">☾</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Start Here</h1>
  <p>This is your roadmap. Follow it step by step — don’t skip.</p>

  <a class="link" href="https://dylan-gorrah.github.io/Java-from-Zero/" target="_blank">
    <div class="title">1. Java From Zero</div>
    <div class="desc">We start simple. Core basics. No shortcuts.</div>
  </a>

  <a class="link" href="https://dylan-gorrah.github.io/road-to-Assignment-part1/" target="_blank">
    <div class="title">2. Road to Assignment</div>
    <div class="desc">Now we level up. Combining logic with structure.</div>
  </a>

  <a class="link" href="https://dylan-gorrah.github.io/Java-Assignment.-ready-doc-from-jframe-to-logic/" target="_blank">
    <div class="title">3. Final Build</div>
    <div class="desc">Putting everything together. Real assignment ready.</div>
  </a>

  <div class="footer">by Dylan Gorrah</div>
</div>

<script>
  function toggleMode() {
    document.body.classList.toggle("light");
  }

  // generate particles
  for (let i = 0; i < 25; i++) {
    const p = document.createElement('div');
    p.className = 'particle';
    p.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
    p.style.animationDuration = (15 + Math.random() * 20) + 's';
    p.style.opacity = Math.random();
    document.body.appendChild(p);
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
